title: Screaming Blue Messiahs - Gun Shy [1986]
description:
This was a fabulous debut full-length from the Screaming Blue Messiahs that featured standouts like "President Kennedy&#039;s Mile," "Smash the Market Place," and "Twin Cadillac Valentine." Not a single bad track here, it would easily rank among my Top 20 for the year.
